{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"user-input","type":"text","text":"# 用户终端输入\n在终端敲下指令并回车","x":0,"y":-1200,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"phase1","type":"text","text":"# 阶段1：终端接收与命令分发\n`entrypoints/cli.tsx` & `/commands`\n\n- CLI 解析 + 预检探针（Node版本/权限/更新）\n- 斜杠命令 `/compact` `/clear` → 本地直接拦截执行\n- 普通对话 → 流转至主引擎\n- 斜杠命令伪装成 AI 回复输出","x":-60,"y":-980,"width":400,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"phase2","type":"text","text":"# 阶段2：环境感知与物理世界挂载\n`context.ts` & `QueryEngine.ts`\n\n- 注入本地时间戳（防幻觉）\n- 自动抓取 `git status` / `git log`\n- 挂载项目 `CLAUDE.md` 知识库\n- UUID 标记请求，计入账单表","x":-60,"y":-660,"width":400,"height":180,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"phase3","type":"text","text":"# 阶段3：提示词预检与缓存折叠\n`microCompact.ts` / `autoCompact.ts`\n\n- 微观清理：删除旧工具超长结果\n- 会话记忆压缩：读取 SESSION_MEMORY.md 替换旧上下文（0延迟）\n- 终极压缩：强制模型生成 `<compacted_summary>` 清空上下文","x":-60,"y":-340,"width":400,"height":180,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"phase4","type":"text","text":"# 阶段4：大模型推理主循环\n`query.ts` : `queryLoop`\n\n- `async function*` 流式生成器\n- 大模型输出 **text** → 即时渲染给终端\n- 大模型输出 **tool_use** → 发起工具调用\n- 超Token自动续写（无损拼接8K+）","x":-60,"y":0,"width":400,"height":180,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"phase7","type":"text","text":"# 阶段7：背景幽灵善后\nPost Sampling Hooks\n\n- 主屏静止后后台触发\n- Fork 纯净分身子代理\n- 结果互不干扰主线程","x":-60,"y":780,"width":400,"height":150,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"output","type":"text","text":"# 终端渲染输出\n\n流式逐字打印 → 用户看到响应\n工具执行状态动画\n记忆保存通知 [X memories saved]","x":-60,"y":1560,"width":400,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"phase5","type":"text","text":"# 阶段5：工具审查与沙盒执行\n`Tool.ts` / Permissions / MCP\n\n- 权限路由引擎：YOLO模式/allow/deny/ask分级\n- yoloClassifier 智能风险打分\n- 沙盒执行：安全操作直接运行\n- 失败自愈：报错文本反馈给 Agent 重试\n- MCP 外部工具协议兼容","x":-440,"y":420,"width":380,"height":220,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tool-module","type":"text","text":"# Tool.ts 工具插槽规范\n\n- `inputSchema` Zod 参数声明\n- `isDestructive()` 破坏性标记\n- `isReadOnly()` / `isConcurrencySafe()`\n- `checkPermissions()` 运行时拦截\n- UI渲染钩子：`renderToolUseMessage`等\n- `buildTool()` 工厂默认值填充\n- MCP 协议兼容","x":-1400,"y":380,"width":360,"height":260,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"prompts-module","type":"text","text":"# SessionMemory/prompts.ts\nPrompt 渲染引擎\n\n- 强制骨架协议（禁改章节标题）\n- Token 字数审计（超12K自动警告）\n- 动态追加恐吓压缩指令\n- 截断器 `truncateSessionMemoryForCompact`\n- 支持用户自定义 `~/.claude/session-memory/config/`","x":-1880,"y":1140,"width":360,"height":240,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"phase6","type":"text","text":"# 阶段6：多轮缠斗与主动完结\n`query.ts` / Stop Reason\n\n- tool_result 返回 → 携新结果再次循环\n- 模型递归思考直到信息足够\n- `stop_reason: end_turn` → 宣布完结","x":340,"y":420,"width":380,"height":180,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"session-memory","type":"text","text":"# 短期会话记忆\n`sessionMemory.ts`\n\n- 监控 Token 开销阈值\n- 后台 Fork 子代理总结\n- 写入 `SESSION_MEMORY.md`\n- 权限锁死：只能写记忆文件\n- 供下次 compact 无延迟复用","x":-960,"y":1140,"width":360,"height":220,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"extract-memories","type":"text","text":"# 长期跨会话记忆\n`extractMemories.ts`\n\n- 发现值得记录的规则/踩坑\n- Fork 只读+专用写权限子代理\n- 写入 `~/.claude/projects/.../memory/`\n- 利用 Prompt Cache 近零成本\n- Ctrl+C 后60秒宽限期确保写完","x":640,"y":1140,"width":360,"height":240,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"permissions-module","type":"text","text":"# 权限路由引擎\n`permissions/`\n\n- `permissionsLoader.ts` 规则加载\n- `permissionRuleParser.ts` 特征匹配\n- YOLO 模式自动放行 (`-y` 标志)\n- `yoloClassifier` 语义风险打分\n- `bypassPermissionsKillswitch` 调试越过\n- allow / deny / ask 三级决策","x":-1400,"y":680,"width":360,"height":260,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"mcp-module","type":"text","text":"# MCP 协议层\nModel Context Protocol\n\n- STDIO / HTTP SSE 双连接模式\n- `initialize` 握手获取 capabilities\n- `tools/list` → 原生 Tool 插槽映射\n- Prompts 聚合 & Resources 读取\n- JSON-RPC 流水线 & 超时容错","x":-1400,"y":100,"width":360,"height":240,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"hooks-module","type":"text","text":"# Hooks 系统\nsettings.json 自动化\n\n- 生命周期 Hooks：pre/post-command\n- 文件访问 Hooks：sessionFileAccess\n- 进程环境 Hooks：subprocessEnv\n- 配置热更新：changeDetector\n- Post Sampling / Stop Hooks 管线","x":640,"y":780,"width":360,"height":220,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"entrypoint-module","type":"text","text":"# entrypoint 入口引导链\n\n- CLI 解析器（commander/yargs）\n- `preflightChecks.tsx` 探针验证\n- CWD 感知 & Settings 加载\n- Session 恢复 & Auth 鉴权\n- React Ink TUI 渲染宿主初始化\n- 引擎交接 → QueryEngine","x":-960,"y":-980,"width":360,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"query-engine","type":"text","text":"# QueryEngine.ts\n会话总调度室\n\n- 持有 `mutableMessages` 完整对话数组\n- 统计 Token 用量 / 美元账单\n- 监控 `maxBudgetUsd` 预算上限\n- 触发 `recordTranscript` 持久化\n- `submitMessage()` 统一入口","x":640,"y":-980,"width":360,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"context-module","type":"text","text":"# context.ts\n物理世界注射站\n\n- `getGitStatus()`：并发抓4条git命令\n- 超2000字符强制截断防污染\n- `getUserContext()`：注入日期+CLAUDE.md\n- `getSystemContext()`：git状态+缓存击穿\n- `memoize` 防止重复扫描","x":640,"y":-690,"width":360,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"compact-module","type":"text","text":"# compact/ 三级防爆体系\n\n**第一级** `microCompact.ts`\n时间断层清理旧工具结果\n\n**第二级** `sessionMemoryCompact.ts`\n读取磁盘摘要文件，0延迟注射\n\n**第三级** `compact.ts` (Legacy)\n单独长调用强制生成 compacted_summary","x":640,"y":-380,"width":360,"height":260,"color":"2"}
	],
